-------------------------------
- JacORB Notification Service -
-------------------------------

you'll need the following libraries

* antlr (version used 2.7.2a6)
  http://www.antlr.org

* util.concurrent (version used 1.3.1)
  http://gee.cs.oswego.edu/dl/classes/EDU/oswego/cs/dl/util/concurrent/intro.html

* log4j (version used 1.2.7)
  http://jakarta.apache.org/log4j
  will be removed

* junit (version used 3.8.1) 
  (only needed for testcases)
  http://www.junit.org

edit 'JacORB/src/org/jacorb/notification/notification_build.properties' to suit the settings on your system 
(a template for unix and windows is supplied).

to compile the notification service:
> cd JacORB/src/org/jacorb/notification
> ant

if you want to run the testcases:
> cd JacORB/test/notification/org/jacorb/notification
> ant

any comments/suggestions to:
Alphonse Bendt <bendt(at)inf.fu-berlin.de>

